						<div class="postbody">Some suggestions:<br /><br />You should initialize the nametable in your program (or turn off background rendering). Also you should generally avoid using non-power-of-two PRG/CHR sizes (in your case you should up the 96 KB CHR to 128 KB).<br /><br />EDIT: of -&gt; off</div>

					
						<div class="postbody"><br />_________________<br /><span style="font-size: 85%; line-height: normal">Download STREEMERZ for NES from <a href="http://www.fauxgame.com" class="postlink">www.fauxgame.com</a>!</span></div>
					
